Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.89,0:00:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 狮堂光与小海、小风三人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.89,0:00:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再度被召唤到异世界锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家现在失去支撑世界的艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面临消灭的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进攻锡菲罗的 欧多札姆的司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了进入王冠的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向拥有钥匙之剑的兰迪斯挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赶到时 兰迪斯的剑发光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人一起被送到王冠的房间外面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我与想得到支柱信物的伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时进入了房间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能成为锡菲罗的支柱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:00:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是伊格尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第44话 小海与泰塔、泰多娜的真枪实战！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支柱的信物…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是为了艾美诺公主的王冠的事而来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的魔法戒指也有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表示能成为支柱的人快产生了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光与伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人都进入了那个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人都平安离开了房间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能成为支柱的只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那两人 都没受到房间的魔法拒绝？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王冠已经开始改变形状
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小光？还是欧多札姆的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底 谁是下一任支柱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯 兰迪斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定又去找小光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 那个女孩有哪里好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是身体比我稍大而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比胸部 我的比较大耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 兰迪斯大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模仿小光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说小光是好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨碍我跟兰迪斯的感情的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是大坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰塔 泰多娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇杰达吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光好像还没醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师古列夫又身体不佳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直不肯说 但…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师古列夫的身体状况 真的很不乐观
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:07:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇杰达进攻锡菲罗的理由 那两位公主已告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此 我还是决定要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能会遇到危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这情况我不能坐视不管
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否危险还不确定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经跟我的朋友约好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于说出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很喜欢阿斯克特哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅与卡尔汀娜、拉法格还有菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都喜欢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:08:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你要保护城堡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我在有人攻击城堡的时候 也可以放心战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风你留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城内还有欧多札姆的司令在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且魔物随时可能出现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有危险时我会马上喊你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑟列斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不留遗憾地去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又得跟奇怪的精灵作战了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不攻击过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙咲海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇杰达的泰塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰多娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以奇杰达王族之名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求和你一战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一战？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我与泰多娜姐姐 要跟你一对一决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是精灵对抗魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是以彼此的实力 做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你赢了的话 我就放弃锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑟列斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事 小海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想相信奇杰达的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许直接打斗很冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想那俩人会光明正大地与我交手的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你顺着心中所相信的 去战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在锡菲罗 信心会成为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑟列斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.73,0:11:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的战士只要有心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一定会以心来回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受你的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里就是决战场所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一对一决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打到有一方不能战斗为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚踩空的话 就会掉下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一场 我是不能够输的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍暴龙卷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要失去战斗能力就好了 不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的 小海不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个换我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰多娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我姐姐很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇杰达没有人敌得过她的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来决斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人很强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里输掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又必须再跟你们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很厉害 不论是身与心…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰多娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧 没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 只是有点吓到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰多娜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你救了这个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的 你不出手救她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也一定会打败我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰多娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甘心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们输了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇杰达 以后不会对锡菲罗出手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后不用再跟你们战斗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也许可以成为好朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你得先改掉粗暴的缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没资格说我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗暴的人就是像你这样的人 你还不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么 怎样 想打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打就打 谁怕谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两人意气相投 感情真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支柱的信物…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始变化了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个沙漏的沙子全部漏光时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗就会崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶在新的支柱诞生之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把锡菲罗的一切 全部消灭才行
